# Environment Variables for Production Backend

## Copy this to your deployment platform (Render/Railway)

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-this-in-production
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=5000

# Cloudinary (for image uploads)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your-cloud-name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your-api-key  
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your-api-secret

# Frontend URL (for CORS)
CLIENT_URL=https://your-app-name.vercel.app

## Instructions:
1. Replace all values with your actual credentials
2. Never commit this file to Git
3. Add these as environment variables in Render/Railway dashboard
